        <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Ketter Home Improvements collects contact and service request information submitted through our website, including name, email, phone number, service address, billing address, and project details.</p>
        <p>This information is used only to review service requests, communicate with customers, schedule work, and manage operations.</p>
        <p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        <p>Information may be used with service providers only as needed to operate our business systems, such as website forms, messaging, and internal workflow tools.</p>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:Robert@Ketter.us">Robert@Ketter.us</a> or call <a href="tel:13045820759">304-582-0759</a>.</p>
